== Changelog ==

= 1.1.1 =
* Fixed SQL error when Featured Slider enabled with no sticky posts and a static front page.

= 1.1 =
* Replaced the old logo uploader with a faster version that uses WP core
* Strip tags from text in the featured slider to prevent breakage
* Hide featured slider unless 2 sticky posts are present
* Upgrade to the latest version of Slides (1.0.2)